    <text x="181" y="126" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle">Test: haklar = hisse → menkul kıymet</text>
    <text x="181" y="158" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="12" text-anchor="middle">Dayanak: Sermaye Piyasaları Kanunu</text>
